Module java.base
Package java.security.acl

Interface Permission

  • @Deprecated(since="9",
            forRemoval=true)
public interface Permission
    Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
    This class is deprecated and subject to removal in a future version of Java SE. It has been replaced by java.security.Policy and related classes since 1.2.
    This interface represents a permission, such as that used to grant a particular type of access to a resource.
    Since:
    1.1
